Job Responsibilities:
   
- Promoting and Selling an exclusive range of products within the B2B, Events or Residential Sales market.
- Engaging with customers in a face to face setting.
- Creating brand/educational experiences.
- Generating sales through product demonstrations and positive interactions.

Skills and Competencies:

- Background in sales, hospitality, retail, and customer service is highly preferred. 
- Proactive, self-motivated and able to function well under pressure.
- Good organisational skills.
- Effective time management.

